      "html": "<p>\"仅仅遵循惯例\"，1833年，来自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of conventional \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/conventional\">conventional</a> + <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -ism \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-ism\">-ism</a>。</p>"
